           fhir:v "Upon the return of hardware, hardware should not be x-rayed or stowed/shipped with radioactive material. Dosimeters should be transported inside lead-lined bags. If X-ray is necessary for security, the dosimeters must be kept inside the lead-lined bags and the number of X-rays should be recorded."
